So when we went to Ganapatipule, "Yes," he

28:20.100 --> 28:25.980
said. "This is the one I want to marry." I
was surprised, you see, with all that how

28:25.980 --> 28:32.600
could he say that "I want to marry this girl"?
I said, "Be sure."

28:32.600 --> 28:39.600
"Yes, yes, I'm very sure, I want to marry."
What he told Me that "She's tranquility personified.

28:41.049 --> 28:48.049
I feel so tranquil." She is full of vibrations,
like bag of vibrations. I know that. But I

28:50.520 --> 28:55.390
didn't know how this fellow has felt it. He
has just fallen in love with her, I tell you.

28:55.390 --> 29:01.890
And he says, "She is the most beautiful person
I have met." He doesn't see anything else

29:01.890 --> 29:08.890
that is outside. Later on My own sister said,
"What have You done? What a match!"

29:09.850 --> 29:16.850
So I looked at that girl, and then I started
seeing these points that she's not good looking,

29:17.200 --> 29:24.200
she's not this, but what he said -- she's
tranquility. She is just tranquility. He went

29:24.450 --> 29:31.170
to her village all the way, and he met all
his family and everybody was surprised, such

29:31.170 --> 29:38.170
a handsome looking Englishman of all the things.
And she said [Shri Mataji corrects] he said,

29:39.320 --> 29:46.320
"Mother, she has neutralized all my nonsensical
points. She's so beautiful." And he's really

29:47.580 --> 29:54.580
in love with her.
So that is a sign of a very deep Sahaja yogi

29:54.670 --> 30:01.670
that they don't go after superficial things.
She cooks South Indian food, he loves it.

30:02.900 --> 30:09.900
Whatever she does he loves. He cares for her
very much. And she is neither left-sided,

30:12.520 --> 30:19.520
nor right-sided, she is in the center. So
both of them match each other because spiritually

30:19.950 --> 30:26.950
they are on the same level, very deep, and
that is what we have to be. If we are not

30:29.980 --> 30:36.980
spiritually matched, then the problem comes
in. We have to have proper matching of vibrations.

30:39.770 --> 30:44.120
Of course, we see to it when we marry, I mean
can you imagine, ninety-nine percent marriages

30:44.120 --> 30:51.120
have been successful. And some of the marriages
were mischievously done I know, there were

30:51.140 --> 30:58.140
some mischiefs. But still they have worked
out. Still they are happy people. But some

31:04.500 --> 31:11.500
people are bent upon making their marriage
a problem. Some of them, extremely egoistical,

31:11.620 --> 31:18.620
think no end of themselves, and start making
everybody miserable. What makes them so much

31:21.580 --> 31:28.580
full of ego, I don't know. And they just spoil
their marriages. They become unhappy themselves,

31:30.950 --> 31:37.950
and they make others also unhappy. Now My
husband has never been a Sahaja yogi, never.

31:40.880 --> 31:47.880
Even now, I wouldn't say he is a Sahaja yogi.
Even now. I don't know. But I knew how to

31:48.740 --> 31:55.740
handle him and how to work it out. And I've
managed very well, and he also knows. Always

31:57.919 --> 32:04.919
he says, "You are very moral person; You are
a very noble person." All those things he

32:08.230 --> 32:15.230
says to Me. And all, you see, his saying is
like this that "You are, but You cannot make

32:18.690 --> 32:20.840
others."
I said, "I can, why not?"

32:20.840 --> 32:27.840
First he could not believe that I could transform
people. And now he knows I have transformed.

32:28.419 --> 32:35.419
He said, "They have become angels." And so
that you are now angels.

