33:58.260 --> 34:03.120
If you are racist you cannot be in Sahaja
Yoga, you understand that. We don't believe

34:03.120 --> 34:07.880
in race and religion and all these things
which are separating human beings from one

34:07.880 --> 34:14.880
to another. That is our ideal, that we cannot
have this kind of a nonsense in our society.

34:18.869 --> 34:25.730
And be careful. Watch your children, how they
react to black people. Specially for Australian

34:25.730 --> 34:32.659
children it is being pointed out. So I think
there's something wrong with some people here.

34:32.659 --> 34:39.659
They should just try to find out if we are
by any chance trying to teach them that white

34:40.989 --> 34:47.989
skin is better than the black.
As I told you in the lecture, I hope you have

34:48.549 --> 34:55.549
listened to what I said about the genes. That
it is now found out that two protective genes

34:56.789 --> 35:03.789
that Asians have the white skin don't have
at all. One of them is the right side, another

35:05.930 --> 35:12.930
the left side. So a white skin will take to
