38:41.170 --> 38:48.170
They all went to the hills and some of them
are preserved in Bolivia and all that. And

38:50.190 --> 38:57.190
the revenge has started. From Bolivia all
these horrible drugs are coming. And the whole

38:59.630 --> 39:06.630
of America is just crushed with that. There's
no wisdom, just to think you have fair skin.

