So first thing you must try to understand
that even if there's a trace of racialism

39:49.759 --> 39:56.759
in you, better throw it away. On the contrary,
I think this country has really, real justice

40:00.140 --> 40:06.970
for racists. Justice-wise you must say Australians
know to be really a multicultural society,

40:06.970 --> 40:13.970
and they understand the value of it: what
you have gained through multicultural societies.

40:18.599 --> 40:25.359
There's so many things to be learned, that
they are very clean, outside, not in personal

40:25.359 --> 40:30.739
life. They'll keep the house very clean, the
carpets very clean, everything very clean,

40:30.739 --> 40:36.170
but as far as themselves are concerned, they
are not so clean. Of course, now with Sahaja

40:36.170 --> 40:41.460
Yoga you are changed, I am not saying.
But I know of English people, they would not

40:41.460 --> 40:48.460
take bath for months, months, they used to
smell like hell. And when My husband was there

40:49.410 --> 40:55.400
we used to shake hands, and the hands would
smell for days together. We used to put scent,

40:55.400 --> 41:01.719
attar, this, that, but still. Using paper,
paper, it's all right because it is very cold,

41:01.719 --> 41:08.719
but it's not that cold. We have lived in England
for so many years. We always use water and

41:10.529 --> 41:17.529
running water. In the same tub, three, four
people take bath, to save pounds. The only

41:17.700 --> 41:24.700
mantra they know is "save pounds". Same here,
people are extremely money-oriented when they

41:26.109 --> 41:33.109
have so much money compared to others. So,
for Sahaja yogis, is important that you should

41:38.180 --> 41:45.180
be frugal and you should not be miserly. You
need not. But you should be clean inside.

41:46.880 --> 41:52.670
That's very important, not outside so much
because see all these diseases are coming,

41:52.670 --> 41:56.589
these things are coming, one has to be very
careful.

41:56.589 --> 42:02.059
Secondly, you are so protective of yourself,
I mean you are always thinking about yourself.

42:02.059 --> 42:08.749
Extremely protective. So you do not develop
any immunity to anything. If you have to travel

42:08.749 --> 42:13.269
like Me, you would get sick within one month's
time. Firstly you can't eat anything, you

42:13.269 --> 42:19.869
get hepatitis. If you smell something you
get hay fever. You do that, I mean all these

42:19.869 --> 42:26.430
things are coming because of over-protectiveness.
You must make your children to play in sand;

42:26.430 --> 42:33.430
you must make them go about. No -- so protective
of your children! So when they grow they cannot

42:34.380 --> 42:41.380
stand anything which is absolutely not completely,
we can say, covered. But Indians don't get

42:47.249 --> 42:54.249
it. We are full of parasites, full of mosquitoes,
full of this. Australian children, when they

42:54.259 --> 43:01.259
got bitten by mosquitoes, they got malaria.
But the whole city was there, nobody got malaria.

43:01.900 --> 43:07.880
Not one person. Now they were surprised, how
is it these boys and girls have got malaria?

43:07.880 --> 43:14.880
So in childhood, we should not make our children
sort of all the time extremely delicate. You

43:16.829 --> 43:23.829
look all right. I mean, might have good muscles
to look at. But you are very, very vulnerable

43:26.940 --> 43:33.249
to any disease. You can see from your children.
I'm not saying about Australians. All the

43:33.249 --> 43:40.249
people from the West, whether they are Americans
or they are Europeans or they are this. But

43:41.339 --> 43:48.339
I've seen Russia, people are very, very good.
They don't catch much. They don't suffer from

43:49.359 --> 43:55.940
all this.
So this over-protectiveness, and also there

43:55.940 --> 44:01.160
are books and books. Today they'll write a
book about children, "You must give them feed

44:01.160 --> 44:07.269
at the right time." Then they will write next
time, "No, no you should not do that way.

44:07.269 --> 44:13.960
You should allow them to eat whatever they
like." Then thirdly they'll say that "You

44:13.960 --> 44:17.170
should not give this to your children, that
you should not give, that should not happen."

44:17.170 --> 44:24.170
With all this knowledge, people are not aware
that they are making their children like the

44:28.019 --> 44:34.920
dolls in the hands of these writers. Whatever
they say, whatever they do, there's no sense

44:34.920 --> 44:41.549
in it. We know what is needed for the children
in Sahaja Yoga. Actually these are people

44:41.549 --> 44:45.200
just selling their books, you know, whatever
knowledge they have, they have a flair to

44:45.200 --> 44:52.200
write, they write it and you accept it and
you get into problems. And this is a very,

44:52.499 --> 44:59.489
very common thing. They protect the children
too much which they need not. But whenever

44:59.489 --> 45:06.489
it is necessary one should.
My main thing is that before the children

45:07.420 --> 45:14.420
how we should behave. There are differences
in husband and wife, not that there are none.

45:15.339 --> 45:22.289
But they should not be exposed. Children should
not be exposed to your differences, to your

45:22.289 --> 45:28.289
fights, to your angers and fits. They get
it; they are so, I am again saying, they are

45:28.289 --> 45:35.289
so protected. So much protection is given
to them. These protected children take these

45:35.940 --> 45:42.940
things very quickly. If mother says to the
father something, father says to the mother,

45:44.460 --> 45:50.710
they'll repeat it later on. You will be surprised,
same thing. When the father does something,

45:50.710 --> 45:57.710
they'll say same thing. So you are spoiling
their whole attitude towards life. Must understand,

46:00.160 --> 46:07.160
children are much faster than you are in picking
up things because they have to learn, they

46:11.779 --> 46:17.150
are growing up.
So your relationship between you and your

46:17.150 --> 46:24.150
wife should be of respect, should be of love
and understanding and caring. But there should

46:29.519 --> 46:36.519
not be something of ... some sort of a scene
that is not good for them. I mean, that doesn't

46:42.469 --> 46:49.229
mean that you behave in a funny manner before
the children. That is for the bedroom, all

46:49.229 --> 46:55.259
right? Thank God, you have bedrooms separate.
We don't even have that. In India, very few

46:55.259 --> 47:02.259
people have bedrooms closed. In the day time,
if they close bedrooms, people think, "Are

47:02.749 --> 47:09.749
they mad or sick?" So this is the attitude
that one has to take that before others, before

47:10.969 --> 47:17.969
other people, before the children and everything,
we have to behave. Now if you want to find

47:19.380 --> 47:26.380
faults with each other, you can find it in
the bedroom. That's not a very good game I

47:27.900 --> 47:32.269
think, why should you find? It's always better
to close the chapter at the end of the day

47:32.269 --> 47:38.969
and sleep well. All this I am telling you
that you should not miss the point of joy

47:38.969 --> 47:45.690
and happiness. This is how you will really
enjoy your children, your husband, your wife,

47:45.690 --> 47:51.690
everything. In this, as I have always said
that the wife has to be very wise. She's the

47:51.690 --> 47:56.940
one who has to be very wise. But not to such
an extent that she allows her husband to do

47:56.940 --> 47:57.690
what he likes. She has to keep a control,
in a way, that he doesn't disturb the society

47:57.690 --> 47:58.180
of Sahaja Yoga.
About other things, like we have about, they

47:58.180 --> 48:02.160
said, I didn't know that you are paying some
money for the school and all those people

48:02.160 --> 48:02.529
who are not even having children in the school
are paying. I didn't know this. School has

48:02.529 --> 48:08.799
money, no doubt. There's no problem on that
because they are not spending much. But now

48:08.799 --> 48:15.799
you change the pattern. I'll talk to your
leader, and see. And also you can have a proper

48:16.630 --> 48:23.630
house on rent, separately and get all the
children there to study, and nobody should

48:24.660 --> 48:31.660
act arbitrarily. And it should be done properly.
I'll talk to your leader and tell him. And

48:32.420 --> 48:39.420
the children should be seen, even by the leaders,
to see that they don't become racist or they

48:40.930 --> 48:47.930
do not become violent. And I think Indian
teachers would be a better idea, because you

48:48.999 --> 48:55.700
see they, they are mild people and it would
be better. And I have also discovered you

48:55.700 --> 49:00.680
have two girls who can work, Indian girls.
It's better that they should look after the

49:00.680 --> 49:07.680
children.
And lastly I have to say, I really enjoyed

49:11.140 --> 49:18.140
My stay in Sydney. Really. I don't know why
this was called as Sydney, what was the reason

49:27.559 --> 49:34.549
-- and also in the West they don't have meaning
for every name. But it's a very beautiful

49:34.549 --> 49:41.549
place where so many Sahaja yogis are there.
And I really feel very happy in your company.

49:42.160 --> 49:49.160
I love you and you all love Me. Whatever I
want is your happiness and joy. And please

49:54.789 --> 50:01.789
remember that we are here to enjoy, all of
us. So don't do anything that makes you unhappy,

50:03.989 --> 50:10.369
like having big, big plans, this, that. Not
necessary. There's no need, and if you want

50:10.369 --> 50:16.839
to have you please let Me know. I'll tell
you exactly whether you should do it or not.

50:16.839 --> 50:23.839
Because I don't want you to land up as bankrupts,
or this and that, like madcap people everywhere.

50:24.390 --> 50:31.089
So this is, you have to be careful, you just
inform Me. You let Me know. You can write

50:31.089 --> 50:35.200
to Me that you have such plans and all that,
I'll tell you.

50:35.200 --> 50:40.509
Now this idea of this artist business is,
now that doesn't go into My head, I must say.

50:40.509 --> 50:44.180
They have told Me that they want to get all
the artists together of the world and this

50:44.180 --> 50:51.180
and that. It's a very one-sided attitude to
form, you see. Just a few artists are there,

50:51.880 --> 50:58.880
then they invite them, and they invite here
and a conference start. That sort of a thing

50:59.140 --> 51:03.329
should not be. If there are artists, all right,
there are artists abroad, everywhere they

51:03.329 --> 51:10.079
are. And wherever you can meet them, you can
meet them. But you cannot separate a body

51:10.079 --> 51:13.529
like that, artists are separately, musicians
separately, then you'll have politicians,

51:13.529 --> 51:20.529
then economists, you see.
So that's not Sahaj standard. That's not Sahaj

51:23.499 --> 51:29.269
Yoga, that's the way people live, you see,
they have separately some sort of a thing,

51:29.269 --> 51:36.269
or if not, they can have a organization of,
say broomstick women, something like that.

51:42.450 --> 51:47.329
So we are Sahaja yogis, and we are Sahaja
yogis and Sahaja yogis. If you are artists,

51:47.329 --> 51:53.200
is by the way. If you are musicians, is by
the way. We are Sahaja yogis and Sahaja yogis.

51:53.200 --> 51:59.259
This is one has to remember. Like this the
groups will start. And this clubbing system

51:59.259 --> 52:04.430
has been there in the human nature, has been
there through out. We have been clubbing with

52:04.430 --> 52:10.979
anything. You know, if there's somebody like
the French, they put their spoon the other

52:10.979 --> 52:17.979
way round, you see, spoon and fork like that.
So I said, "Why?"

52:18.440 --> 52:24.299
"Because we're French."
I couldn't understand this explanation, "these

52:24.299 --> 52:30.160
are French". And then the English put it this
way. Now if you just put it the other way

52:30.160 --> 52:37.160
round, I mean, you are a gone case, then you
are no good. So we have to know that this

52:38.539 --> 52:44.489
kind of clubbing was in the human nature because
it comes from the animal instinct. You see

52:44.489 --> 52:51.219
animals also club together. You are from Brisbane?
All right, we sit together. You are from here,

52:51.219 --> 52:58.219
we sit together. It's a animal instinct. Because
of some sort of a fear maybe, that they club

52:58.660 --> 53:03.549
together. This clubbing, clubbing has come
to human race also. For everything you have

53:03.549 --> 53:09.039
a club, you know that.
For you it is not necessary because you have

53:09.039 --> 53:16.039
come out of that state of animal instinct
to higher instincts. Yes, you are an artist.

53:17.180 --> 53:22.219
All right, you are an artist. So another is
an artist, all right. But don't club together

53:22.219 --> 53:28.859
as artists, as musicians, as this, as that.
As long as you have to say sing together,

53:28.859 --> 53:34.329
you can practice, again finished. It's very
important point. Try to understand. Clubbing

53:34.329 --> 53:41.329
is not at all a human quality. Clubbing is
a quality of animals. So when we are all Sahaja

53:43.609 --> 53:49.749
yogis, why should we club together? What is
the need to club? And this clubbing has brought

53:49.749 --> 53:55.559
so much problem to us. This politicians, then
this religions, and all this nothing but clubbing

53:55.559 --> 54:02.559
-- that separates. So anytime you find there's
a clubbing system working anywhere, just run

54:04.089 --> 54:11.089
away from there. You belong to a very big
community. Now say in My hand, these fingers

54:11.229 --> 54:18.229
start clubbing, what will I do with them?
I'll have to make a club out of it. But still

54:20.700 --> 54:27.700
going on. I mean when they come to Ganapatipule
there had clubs going on there also. I've

54:28.079 --> 54:35.079
been informed about them. Australian club,
and north Australian then south Australians,

54:36.239 --> 54:43.239
then east, west and southeast, southwest,
so all that has to be given up. One has to

54:44.599 --> 54:50.219
understand that we are all Sahaja yogis, all
over the world, wherever we may live, whatever

54:50.219 --> 54:57.219
we may eat, whatever we may wear. We are inside
all Sahaja yogis, and all connected to all-pervading

54:58.900 --> 55:05.900
power. If you become great artistes because
you have got Sahaja Yoga, all right, enjoy

55:06.369 --> 55:11.140
that. If you became great musicians, all right,
enjoy that. If you become an orator, enjoy

55:11.140 --> 55:18.140
that. But you don't club yourself with another
person on those grounds. That is something

55:19.069 --> 55:26.069
not at all Sahaj. In Sahaj you are one with
every one, and with all of them.

55:26.949 --> 55:33.469
See now, My life if it is anything, you should
understand that I am extremely a sahaj person,

55:33.469 --> 55:39.849
extremely sahaj. So wherever I go, I can't
understand. I go to Russia, all these Russians,

55:39.849 --> 55:46.849
they had never known about Me, they have never
heard about Me, they came to listen to Me.

55:47.069 --> 55:52.900
Anywhere I go. I mean later on the follow
up may not be that good, but wherever I go

55:52.900 --> 55:59.900
there are in thousands of people. After all
what is so great about Me? See this is it.

56:02.380 --> 56:08.920
What you have to learn -- I am so sahaj and
also when I tell you about, you don't feel

56:08.920 --> 56:15.619
bad. Because you know, you know I am telling
you out of compassion and love, and that is

56:15.619 --> 56:22.170
important. You understand that because first
thing is compassion and love. And when there

56:22.170 --> 56:27.140
is compassion and love, you cannot think of
clubbing at all, never. You can never club

56:27.140 --> 56:33.680
with anyone. You will love each and every
person, and be kind and enjoy your compassion,

56:33.680 --> 56:36.640
the virtue of your compassion, virtue of your
love.

56:36.640 --> 56:43.640
And that is, that shows on your faces, you
shine compared to those born again, who were

56:44.029 --> 56:51.029
never born again. They were looking so hazard
and horrible, very harsh faces, with such

56:55.849 --> 57:02.079
a young girl, she had all the wrinkles you
could count on her face, going round and round

57:02.079 --> 57:04.719
and round.
So I told her, "You are not born again, I

57:04.719 --> 57:06.259
am sorry."
She said, "Are You?"

57:06.259 --> 57:11.749
I said, "I am. Look at your face in the mirror.
You will know, you are not born again."

57:11.749 --> 57:18.749
So the greatest advantage of Sahaja Yoga is
that you can enjoy everything. That is the

57:18.989 --> 57:25.989
greatest advantage, whether it is art, architecture,
music, or a lecture, or studies, education,

57:27.989 --> 57:34.989
family life, everything you should be able
to enjoy fully. Then you are a real Sahaja

57:35.890 --> 57:42.209
yogi and that you have achieved that state.
Sometimes there are problems, here and there,

57:42.209 --> 57:49.049
something happens, doesn't matter. Have faith,
and you will be surprised at the miracles

57:49.049 --> 57:56.049
that you get. One after another, so many miracles,
but listen to Me and also try to follow what

57:58.900 --> 58:04.799
I say.
First of all, no temper. Temper if you have,

58:04.799 --> 58:10.059
you must know that it's a serious thing in
the West because there's no controlling power

58:10.059 --> 58:17.059
over temper, and schizophrenia is the only
ultimate result of temper. So temper should

58:19.289 --> 58:26.289
not be justified. All ego, temper should be
brought down. One should not try in any way

58:29.229 --> 58:34.709
to get angry with others because of jealousy,
because of complexes, because of anything.

58:34.709 --> 58:41.709
If it is so, please introspect, "Why do I
get into tempers?" Shri Krishna has placed

58:46.969 --> 58:51.789
temper as the worst disease of all, He said
from there it rises everything. But I don't

58:51.789 --> 58:57.130
agree with Him because, you see, it must be,
He was, for Him it's a leela, the whole world

58:57.130 --> 59:04.130
is a leela, but not for everyone. Temper can
come from Mooladhara, can come from Swadishtana,

59:04.769 --> 59:11.769
can come from anywhere. So one cannot say
that the source of temper is going to be the

59:13.519 --> 59:20.519
source of all the problems, can be from anything.
One can really get destroyed by anything,

59:20.880 --> 59:26.009
but temper is one thing that is the worst
of all.

59:26.009 --> 59:33.009
So, if you find anybody who is hot tempered,
if you find yourself to be hot tempered, then

59:33.920 --> 59:40.920
please see to it that you overcome it. I used
to tell before, I don't know now, there must

59:42.579 --> 59:47.289
be My tapes that if you are very angry, then
stand before the mirror and say all kinds

59:47.289 --> 59:54.289
of things. Or else you take a pillow and hit
it hard when you are in temper. Close the

59:55.039 --> 01:00:01.479
door, hit the pillow and then go out. You
may have to spend for another pillow, doesn't

01:00:01.479 --> 01:00:08.479
matter. So you develop a very, I should say,
a pleasing personality. That's very important.

01:00:11.130 --> 01:00:18.130
You must have a very pleasing personality.
But that is not acceptable in certain countries

01:00:25.279 --> 01:00:31.459
because it's said that you should not show
your, any pleasing personality, because others

01:00:31.459 --> 01:00:38.459
will think you are weak. The strength is your
joy. Strength is your virtue, strength is

01:00:40.989 --> 01:00:47.829
your pleasing personality. That is your strength.
And this artificially, some people say that

01:00:47.829 --> 01:00:52.630
if you become very pleasing and this and that,
then others will think you are weak. If they

01:00:52.630 --> 01:00:59.630
think, let them think like that. That is their
stupidity. So you should be happy, joyous,

01:01:00.219 --> 01:01:05.930
pleasing.
I must say in Sahaja Yoga some people have

01:01:05.930 --> 01:01:12.930
come up so well that I really feel very proud
of them, very proud. And also, I never expected

01:01:14.299 --> 01:01:21.299
this to work out so well in My lifetime, I
never expected because I started it very late,

01:01:23.190 --> 01:01:30.190
deliberately. So it is very heartening to
see so many Sahaja yogis coming up, and listening

01:01:30.880 --> 01:01:37.880
to Me so nicely without taking any objection
to what I say, and then imbibing it in their

01:01:40.660 --> 01:01:45.279
lives so that they can enjoy themselves very
well.

01:01:45.279 --> 01:01:52.279
This time I had to meet people separately
and in one room and all, but next time I think

01:01:55.259 --> 01:02:00.329
I'll discuss certain problems openly. If you
people are doing something stupid which, let

01:02:00.329 --> 01:02:07.329
us, all of us know. So that there'll be some
fear of people who are doing wrong things.

01:02:07.569 --> 01:02:14.569
For example, I don't know is he here, Peter
Patten, is he here? He's not here? Peter Patten

01:02:17.739 --> 01:02:24.739
from Adelaide. He has been very funny, and
he has to get out of Sahaja Yoga I think,

01:02:29.349 --> 01:02:36.349
for some time.
Then there's one Mark, is he here? Where is

01:02:37.569 --> 01:02:44.569
he? Just call him. So you see, he doesn't
realize what's wrong with him. And he is trying

01:02:48.910 --> 01:02:55.619
to force himself on to others. Is not a very
good idea. You all take a bandhan, I think

01:02:55.619 --> 01:03:02.619
you see, it's all right. Where is he? So we
will have a open talk about it, so you will

01:03:13.589 --> 01:03:20.589
realize what's wrong with the person. Extremely
right-sided is, the whole thing is burning.

01:03:28.890 --> 01:03:35.890
Where is he? What's the matter with you? Why
do you want to meet Me?

01:03:48.759 --> 01:03:55.759
[Mark: I was just going to get some directions
from You, Shri Mataji.]

01:04:03.499 --> 01:04:05.479
What direction?
[Mark: Just about what I should be doing,

01:04:05.479 --> 01:04:09.319
as far as more involvement in ....]
I mean, just think of it, if I have to talk

01:04:09.319 --> 01:04:11.650
to each person like that, what will be My
situation?

01:04:11.650 --> 01:04:17.150
[Mark: Yes Shri Mataji.]
So why should you force your way like that?

01:04:17.150 --> 01:04:24.150
You could have written a letter to Me, I would
have known whatever you wanted. You see, now

01:04:24.509 --> 01:04:30.999
try to understand what's your problem is.
Your problem is right side. All right? Sit

01:04:30.999 --> 01:04:37.999
down and remove it. That's your problem. You
can find it out very easily, what your problem

01:04:38.239 --> 01:04:43.009
is, and which you can solve. You can also
talk to the leaders but you have to be humble

01:04:43.009 --> 01:04:49.390
about it. You should not be aggressive. "I
must meet Mataji, I must meet Mataji." You

01:04:49.390 --> 01:04:56.390
see, supposing you all want to meet Me individually,
what will happen? And you will be amazed only

01:04:58.599 --> 01:05:03.589
in Sydney I meet people like this. Only I
have been meeting and meeting and meeting.

01:05:03.589 --> 01:05:10.589
For that, now I would say that you should
tell your leaders first. Let them scan you

01:05:10.979 --> 01:05:16.719
out, let them write what are their problems
are. Then if I want to see, I'll see. I should

01:05:16.719 --> 01:05:23.719
have that much freedom. You can't force things
on Me, can you? I have not taken a contract

01:05:27.930 --> 01:05:34.569
with you or anything. So all of you who want
to see Me, should not talk to Vinay, because

01:05:34.569 --> 01:05:41.219
he's now fed up. He's so tired, he doesn't
know. Everybody is pressurizing him. So now

01:05:41.219 --> 01:05:46.469
please tell your leader. Leader has to give
Me your problems. Then I'll see, if I want

01:05:46.469 --> 01:05:53.469
to see or if I don't want to see. We have
to stop this. There's nothing special, nothing

01:05:57.650 --> 01:06:04.650
great that you cannot tell the leader. The
leader can solve your problem. Because I have

01:06:05.759 --> 01:06:12.759
to go from countries to counties, you know
that. Even in Australia, I travel from cities

01:06:16.569 --> 01:06:23.569
to city, which I do not do in anywhere. Even
in India, only two places I go to or only

01:06:25.609 --> 01:06:32.609
the capital. But I feel concerned about you.
You have gone through bumpy areas.

01:06:34.359 --> 01:06:38.559
But try to understand that there's no contract
with Me. If you have come to Sahaja Yoga,

01:06:38.559 --> 01:06:45.559
doesn't mean that you have right to do what
you like. No. I must cure, I must touch person,

01:06:47.499 --> 01:06:54.049
I must see. This is too much. What have you
done for Sahaja Yoga. Ask this question, "What

01:06:54.049 --> 01:07:01.049
have I done for Sahaja Yoga? How many people
I have given realization?" I've been just

01:07:03.140 --> 01:07:09.910
fighting with others, having family problems,
this, that or "Have I done anything which

01:07:09.910 --> 01:07:16.839
is constructive to help Mother?" As you know,
My age is now seventy-one, I don't know how

01:07:16.839 --> 01:07:19.900
far My husband will allow Me to travel now,
also. Whatever it is.

01:07:19.900 --> 01:07:25.869
You have to take over. You have to take the
responsibility. You have all the powers, you

01:07:25.869 --> 01:07:32.869
have all the knowledge. You are quite all
right now for Sahaja Yoga spreading. So go

01:07:34.660 --> 01:07:41.660
ahead. You are wise enough to understand that
now we should spare our Mother. So nobody

01:07:45.339 --> 01:07:51.579
should be aggressive like that. All right?
If I have to see somebody, I will see. But

01:07:51.579 --> 01:07:56.809
first of all you must tell your leaders and
give them the full reason why you want to

01:07:56.809 --> 01:08:02.309
see Me, and if I think it proper, I'll see.
This much freedom you should give Me that

01:08:02.309 --> 01:08:09.309
if I want, I'll see you. There is some sort
of a protocol is there for people that they

01:08:17.109 --> 01:08:24.109
should understand that you cannot just ask
to see Me just like that.

01:08:28.790 --> 01:08:35.790
As you love Me, you can feel for Me also and
understand that what is important is you should

01:08:37.059 --> 01:08:44.059
go deep down into yourself and I am there.
I am there, absolutely. I am everywhere. You

01:08:46.559 --> 01:08:53.559
need not see My face or see Me. I am there.
Just know this fact that I am there with you

01:08:53.609 --> 01:09:00.609
all the time whether you write to Me, whether
you inform Me or not. There are people who

01:09:00.989 --> 01:09:07.839
have developed such, such tremendous faith
that Mother is everywhere, that just by praying

01:09:07.839 --> 01:09:14.839
they have saved the lives of people. Just
from praying. There are many like that. And

01:09:16.259 --> 01:09:22.429
really, it is worth seeing these people, how
simple they are. I won't even see them normally,

01:09:22.429 --> 01:09:29.429
anywhere. But they are there. And they told
Me how they have achieved so many things so

01:09:30.400 --> 01:09:37.400
easily. It is very remarkable.
There was one fellow whose mother was sick

01:09:38.480 --> 01:09:45.480
in Rohtak and he was in, I think, Bombay and
he received a message that she is sick and

01:09:47.239 --> 01:09:52.250
she will die very soon. So he rushed to the
place and they told him that within three

01:09:52.250 --> 01:09:58.179
days she will be finished. His mother is not
a realized soul nor she's a Sahaja yogini,

01:09:58.179 --> 01:10:05.030
she has never even seen Me. He said, "Mother
I couldn't help it. I just went on my knees

01:10:05.030 --> 01:10:12.030
and I just prayed, 'oh Mother, please can
You save my mother?'" Within three days the

01:10:12.559 --> 01:10:18.340
lady got all right. They said it's a galloping
cancer. He flew her to Bombay and took her

01:10:18.340 --> 01:10:25.190
to the Tata hospital to find out if there
is any cancer. They said, "There's no trace

01:10:25.190 --> 01:10:32.190
of cancer." He said, "This is the last time
I have asked You for anything." I just, I

01:10:34.559 --> 01:10:41.559
just -- it has happened with many.
So it is your faith. Faith is not blind in

01:10:43.280 --> 01:10:49.230
Sahaja Yoga, you know for definite what is
Sahaja Yoga is. You have seen miraculous photographs.

01:10:49.230 --> 01:10:53.980
You have seen all the miracles happening.
So now your faith should be completely, entirely

01:10:53.980 --> 01:11:00.980
in it. And it will work out. I promise you
if your faith is deep enough to reach Me,

01:11:02.679 --> 01:11:03.980
you don't have to see My face, even not to
have My photograph, nothing. Wherever you

01:11:03.980 --> 01:11:04.270
are, you'll find Me. That's why I always say,
"Develop your faith, develop your faith."

01:11:04.270 --> 01:11:04.429
May God bless you!
May God bless you!

01:11:04.429 --> 01:11:05.880
So thank you again and again for all these
flowers and for all the nice time I had here.

01:11:05.880 --> 01:11:05.889
it.
