01:11:05.889 --> 01:11:05.900
especially when Shri Mataji is reprimanding
some yogis (mark), the transcribing team has

01:11:05.900 --> 01:11:05.909
nevertheless included this content not knowing
whether it should really be excluded.So, thank

01:11:05.909 --> 01:11:05.920
you very much for the greetings on this day.
It was a Easter Monday when I got married

01:11:05.920 --> 01:11:05.929
always changes according to the Monday it
comes.

01:11:05.929 --> 01:11:05.940
So it was quite a big venture for Me to marry.
Actually, I did not need it at all. But as

01:11:05.940 --> 01:11:06.050
you know in India, they won't spare any girl
from marriage, and they have been after My

01:11:06.050 --> 01:11:06.110
life since I was about eighteen years of age.
So somehow I managed. But I was in the medical

01:11:06.110 --> 01:11:06.159
college Lahore, and suddenly the disturbances
broke out of a very serious nature. And I

01:11:06.159 --> 01:11:06.219
came back, and there was no possibility of
My going back. Then the whole thing planned,

01:11:06.219 --> 01:11:06.280
I think Divine planned it for My marriage,
because I had to accept them. And as My husband

01:11:06.280 --> 01:11:06.329
was there, there were many proposals also,
which they chose this one, and I was married.

01:11:06.329 --> 01:11:06.400
In a way arranged, because I had never talked
to him about it, he had not talked to Me,

01:11:06.400 --> 01:11:06.449
but he had seen Me once before.
So for Me it was all right because everybody

01:11:06.449 --> 01:11:06.510
so much worried in My family about My marriage
all the time. Throughout I feel that I looked

01:11:06.510 --> 01:11:06.570
after My husband's relations, family, though
he had none. He had only one sister whose

01:11:06.570 --> 01:11:06.619
grandson is Vinay. And all the rest of the
family, all those relations of his, I really

01:11:06.619 --> 01:11:06.670
looked after them. And he was counting, he
said, "You have looked after thirty-five nephews,"

01:11:06.670 --> 01:11:06.909
only nephews and how many nieces and how many?
Because it was nature, you see, of compassion,

01:11:06.909 --> 01:11:06.909
was well placed in life because he had never
bothered about his lands and things. So he

01:11:07.690 --> 01:11:08.559
came for the wedding of My granddaughter,
and also of My daughters, and showed their

01:11:08.559 --> 01:11:09.329
gratitude. Out of them very few have come
to Sahaja Yoga. Actually, the relations are

01:11:09.329 --> 01:11:10.000
always like that. They are so close that I
tell them there's a black point, you know,

01:11:10.000 --> 01:11:10.050
where everything dissolves into zero. So they
are so close that they cannot see what is

01:11:10.050 --> 01:11:10.090
Sahaja Yoga. They have tremendous regard for
Me. They have tremendous respect for Me. They

01:11:10.090 --> 01:11:10.139
will do anything, especially My husband has
spent lot of money in the beginning of Sahaja

01:11:10.139 --> 01:11:10.190
Yoga, quite a lot. He doesn't ask for it;
he never mentioned it also. And we has spent

01:11:10.190 --> 01:11:10.239
so much of his money. We had a joint account;
he never questioned Me, nothing of the kind.

01:11:10.239 --> 01:11:10.280
Very sweet of him.
So the situation is better now. They have

01:11:10.280 --> 01:11:10.329
faith in Sahaja Yoga. They try to meditate
also. But they are not seekers, in a way,

01:11:10.329 --> 01:11:10.380
because they are so close to Me. As you people
have an advantage, great advantage you have

01:11:10.380 --> 01:11:10.420
that firstly you are seekers from ages, and
you understand how important it is to get

01:11:10.420 --> 01:11:10.469
your Self-realization, because you feel lost
without it. You think that if you don't get

01:11:10.469 --> 01:11:10.510
your Self-realization, you should commit suicide,
and there are many letters I have got saying

01:11:10.510 --> 01:11:10.559
that "We were mad. We were seeking, going
to this person, going to that person." Such

01:11:10.559 --> 01:11:10.860
big, big letters I got from them how they
were cheated, how they were tortured, and

01:11:10.860 --> 01:11:11.010
how they had spent money and how they were
completely lynched by these gurus. Some of

01:11:11.010 --> 01:11:11.150
them had to sell their houses, and children
were, they moved from schools, and everybody

01:11:11.150 --> 01:11:11.300
became extremely poor. So this was in London
much worse. Later on I found that every country

01:11:11.300 --> 01:11:11.400
has this problem, they became drug addicts
and all that.

01:11:11.400 --> 01:11:11.630
Despite all that now we have so many people
who are Sahaja Yogis all over the world, not

01:11:11.630 --> 01:11:11.929
only in Australia. But Australia has quite
a lot of Sahaja Yogis, I must say. And quantity

01:11:11.929 --> 01:11:12.040
is very, very large and good, and people are
nice, but we have had, as I told you, a very

01:11:12.040 --> 01:11:12.139
bumpy start. Because of that, certain conditionings
are built up in people. But now we have to

01:11:12.139 --> 01:11:12.300
see that our quality has to improve. Quality
has to improve, and the test of quality, I

01:11:12.300 --> 01:11:12.300
the artists together of the world and this
and that. It's a very one-sided attitude to
